Circuit Systems Inc said it hasbought all of the stock of (Ionic Industries Inc) in exchangefor 3,677,272 shares of its common.    Following the exchange there will be 4,969,643 shares ofCircuit Systems stock outstanding. Ionic holders will own about74 pct of the outstanding stock of Circuit Systems, it said.    Ionic, a maker of circuit boards, had revenues of 8.4 mlndlrs and pretax profits of 232,000 dlrs in 1986, up fromrevenues of 5.9 mln and pretax profits of 204,000 dlrs in 1985,Circuit Systems said. Reuter&#3;